drawal, or similar payment device that is received by the holder in connection with the contract and that is returned for nonpayment for any reason. 500 copies of this document were printed by the South Dakota Legislative Research Council at a cost of $.021 per page. . Insertions into existing statutes are indicated by underscores. Deletions from existing statutes are indicated by overstrikes."}, {"bill_id": 15599, "bill_version_id": 86921, "bill_version": "Enrolled", "bill_version_date": "2000-02-17T00:00:00-06:00", "bill_text": ""}], "amendments": [], "fiscal_notes": [], "action_log": [{"bill_id": 15599, "action_date": "2000-01-24T14:00:00-06:00", "document_id": 85639, "document_url": "https://mylrc.sdlegislature.gov/api/Documents/85639.pdf", "status_text": "First read in Senate and referred to", "journal_page": 165, "committee_id_action": 657, "committee_id_assigned": 631, "result": "N", "vote": {}}, {"bill_id": 15599, "action_date": "2000-02-01T10:00:00-06:00", "document_id": 85834, "document_url": "https://mylrc.sdlegislature.gov/api/Documents/85834.pdf", "status_text": "Scheduled for Committee hearing on this date", "journal_page": null, "committee_id_action": 631, "committee_id_assigned": null, "result": "N", "vote": {}}, {"bill_id": 15599, "action_date": "2000-02-01T10:00:00-06:00", "document_id": 85834, "document_url": "https://mylrc.sdlegislature.gov/api/Documents/85834.pdf", "status_text": "Do Pass,", "journal_page": 268, "committee_id_action": 631, "committee_id_assigned": null, "result": "P", "vote": {"vote_id": 45737, "president_vote": null, "Yea": [2365, 2380, 2381, 2399, 2405, 2320, 2391]}}, {"bill_id": 15599, "action_date": "2000-02-01T10:00:00-06:00", "document_id": 85834, "document_url": "https://mylrc.sdlegislature.gov/api/Documents/85834.pdf", "status_text": "Place on Consent Calendar", "journal_page": null, "committee_id_action": 631, "committee_id_assigned": null, "result": "P", "vote": {}}, {"bill_id": 15599, "action_date": "2000-02-02T14:00: